<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>حم <span class="c2">(١)</span> عسق <span class="c2">(٢)</span> كَذَلِكَ يُوحِي إِلَيْكَ وَإِلَى الَّذِينَ مِنْ قَبْلِكَ اللَّهُ الْعَزِيزُ الْحَكِيمُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>